{"word":"ὁδεύω","slug":"ὁδεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ὁδεύω</b></el> <el>(ὁδεύω,) ( φυτ. <el>-σω</el>) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>ὁδός</el>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to go, travel</i>, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a> <i>to be provided with thoroughfares</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}